    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom-grade condition, reflecting a standard of maintenance reserved for the most discerning collectors. Every surface and mechanical component has been preserved to an exacting degree, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its initial release. For the professional who demands excellence without compromise, this acquisition represents a rare opportunity to secure a benchmark-quality asset.",
